This project focuses on the tools and processes for quickly turning on
production quality web sites.  

Key technologies include:
 *  Django
 *  Python
 *  MySQL
 *  Linux 
 *  Web Faction hosting
 *  Emacs

Technical capabilities:
 *  Web site 
 *  Standard navigation
 *  CSS
 *  Forms process
 *  Database updates


See also [[Brain]], WebDevelopmentPlatform


